title: BONUS EPISODE: BTS at our iHeartRadio Music Festival
itunes:title: BONUS EPISODE: BTS at our iHeartRadio Music Festival
description:
This episode was recorded backstage at our iHeartRadio Music Festival in Las Vegas. Bobby, Amy, Lunchbox and Eddie talk about the journey to the festival, some behind the scenes stories from previous years, we play a fun music game with Lunchbox and much more!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
